*** TI-86 CHEMISTRY PROGRAMS: /pub/graph-ti/calc-apps/86/science/chemistry/

bvc
---
The BVC program performs all bond valence calculations needed to successfully 
work through an inorganic crystal structure in terms of atomic valences 
(oxidation states), bond strengths, comparisons with idealized structures, etc.

chem
----
An assortment of chemistry programs.

pvnrt
-----
PVNRT is a chemistry program used for finding pressure, temp, moles, etc.

vaph2o
------
This program gives the vapor pressure of water in mmHg (same as torr) for any 
integer temperature between 15 and 35 degrees Celcius.


